edu.cnm.deepdive.ironorimgtransform.model.entity

Class Transform

  • java.lang.Object
    • edu.cnm.deepdive.ironorimgtransform.model.entity.Transform

  • public class Transform
extends Object
    Encapsulates the attributes of a single image transformation algorithm. Room and GSon annotations are used to specify entity & attribute mapping for database persistence, and property mapping for JSON serialization/deserialization mapping.
